description: The Coconut Truck is a SoCal food truck offering Cambodian-inspired street food with a modern twist. Specializing in nom pang (Cambodian sandwiches) we craft our food to be fresh, savory and packed with delicious flavor. Our sandwiches are hand-crafted and made-to-order with high-quality produce, freshly baked artisanal bread, all natural cuts of meat and vibrant, aromatics, herbs and spices.
name: The Coconut Truck
